name: Kung Fu Superstar: Become the Ultimate Martial Arts Stuntman
blurb: Become the most popular Martial Arts stuntman Hollywood has ever known, while learning real Kung Fu techniques and fighting in movies!

rewards.reward: No Reward

ENTHUSIAST (WHITE SASH REWARD): All backers pledging at this level and above get an account for our exclusive backer forums, where you can stay on top of the developments around the game before anyone else and engage with the community and the development team. You also get a special thank you credit on our website.
FLASH-BACKER: *FLASH SALE* Limited version of the BACKER reward! Grab them while they last! (Approx. $16)
BACKER (WHITE SASH REWARD): Digital Download of the finished Kung Fu Superstar: Origin game on PC
GRASSHOPPER (WHITE SASH REWARD): Previous Tiers + Digital Download of the game's Original Soundtrack + Digital Download of the "Art of Kung Fu Superstar" book

CINEPHILE (WHITE SASH REWARD): 

Previous Tiers + Poster from the game

You get a choice between a poster of the actual game or a movie style poster of one of the movies in the game! Kungfuception!

CURATOR (WHITE SASH REWARD): 

If you're like us and you get a warm fuzzy feeling when you organise your games library this one's for you. 

A physical high quality digipack style box that includes a DVD of the game, a CD of the game's Original Soundtrack and the game's manual
FLASH-KUNG FU ADEPT: *FLASH SALE* Limited version of the KUNG FU ADEPT reward! Grab them while they last! (Approx. $48)

DISCIPLE (WHITE SASH REWARD): 

Previous Tiers (So yes, that means both a digital AND the digipack physical copy) + Beta Access to the game.

Get to play Kung Fu Superstar: Origin before anyone else and actively contribute in the development of the game

KUNG FU ADEPT: 

Previous Tiers + a physical copy of the full scale Kung Fu Superstar game, when that gets released, for a platform of your choice (PC/Console). 

For your early support and long term commitment to the Kung Fu Superstar vision, you get both Kung Fu Superstar: Origin AND Kung Fu Superstar for the price of ONE game (plus all the other goodies)

OUTFITTER (BROWN SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nStylish high quality "Kung Fu Superstar" T-Shirt exclusive to this Kickstarter campaign developed in collaboration with select video games apparel partners + GRASSHOPPER Reward

MONK (BROWN SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nStylish high quality "Kung Fu Superstar" Hoodie exclusive to this Kickstarter campaign developed in collaboration with select video games apparel partners + GRASSHOPPER Reward

STUNTMAN (BROWN SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nSigned copy of the book "Fight Choreography: The Art of Non Verbal Dialogue" by Stuntman and Fight Coordinator John Kreng, the definitive textbook for Fight Choreography in action cinema + GRASSHOPPER Reward

SCHOLAR (BROWN SASH REWARD): 

Copy of the book "Kung Fu Superstar: Development Diaries", the definitive source of insight into the intrigue, suspense, thrill and romance behind the making of this game + GRASSHOPPER Reward. 

Actually it might be lighter on the romance and heavier on incredible true anecdotal stories that happened during the development of the project. Some of which include romance.
SCULPTOR (BROWN SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nLimited Edition "Danny Cheng" Figurine exclusive to this Kickstarter campaign + GRASSHOPPER Reward

CALLIGRAPHIST (BROWN SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nLimited Edition, high quality, hard cover, physical copy of "The Art of Kung Fu Superstar" book, with exclusive additional content to the PDF version + GRASSHOPPER Reward

MNEMONIC COURIER (BROWN SASH REWARD): 

A Limited Edition custom made 16GB USB Flash Drive in the shape of a Baat Jaam Dao, the iconic Chinese "Butterfly Sword", preloaded with the items from the GRASSHOPPER Reward. 

Stylish as well as functional. Be the envy of your friends or challenge them to minitature sword fights.
FLASH-MASTER: *FLASH SALE* Limited version of the KUNG FU MASTER Reward! Grab them while they last! (Approx. $145)

KUNG FU MASTER: 

Incredible value LIMITED Reward Tier for early and long term supporters of the Kung Fu Superstar vision. A physical copy of the full scale Kung Fu Superstar game, when that gets released, for a platform of your choice (PC/Console) + ALL WHITE SASH Rewards + 2 BROWN SASH Rewards of your choice.

Maximum value for your invaluable support.

GUARDIAN (BLACK SASH REWARD): Limited Edition, 3 piece, elegant Kung Fu outfit exclusive to this Kickstarter campaign + Exclusive "Danny's Locker" In Game Content  (see FAQ for details) + GRASSHOPPER Reward

SWORDMASTER (BLACK SASH REWARD): \r\n\r\nA beautiful Limited Edition, hand crafted pair of hardwood Butterfly Swords exlusive to this Kickstarter campaign + Exclusive "Baat Jaam Dao Forms" In Game Content (see FAQ for details) + GRASSHOPPER Reward

KUNG FU GRANDMASTER: \r\n\r\nThe Ultimate Kung Fu Superstar Reward Tier for Reward Completionists! A physical copy of the full scale Kung Fu Superstar game, when that gets released, for a platform of your choice (PC/Console) + ALL BLACK SASH + ALL WHITE SASH Rewards + 3 BROWN SASH Rewards of your choice + GRANDMASTER Credit in all our games EVER!

KUNG FU LEGEND: So you think the GRANDMASTER Reward is cool, but it's just not LEGENDARY enough for you? Ok, how about this! ALL WHITE SASH Rewards +  ALL BROWN SASH Rewards + ALL BLACK SASH Rewards + All future releases + LEGEND Credit in all our games ever + "Honorary Dev" rights (FAQ for details)

INFILTRATOR: \r\n\r\nJoin in over Video Conference for a team meeting (pick your discipline, design, art, code, etc) and chat with the developers live, ask questions, contribute ideas, give feedback + LEGEND REWARD

IMMORTAL: \r\n\r\nWork together with our character art team to lend your likeness to one of the extras in the game (early adopters of this reward tier will be given more prominent roles, maybe even one of the main bad guys if we think your face is evil enough?) + LEGEND Reward

SHOT ON LOCATION: Video call not good enough for you? Well why don't you come over and join us at the studio for a week? That's right, pledging at this level means that we'll invite you over to the studio for a full working week where you'll join the team meetings and have your own desk and workstation to playtest or even work on the game if you want to. Socialise with the team in the evenings, make friends, have fun! We will pick up your acommodation costs, but you'll have to make your own travel arrangments + IMMORTAL Reward + LEGEND Reward

TOURIST: 

Same as SHOT ON LOCATION only we will ALSO pick up both your accommodation and travel costs. 

ALSO the time of your visit will coincide with the game's EXTRAVAGANT launch party to which you will receive a +1 invitation. 

ALSO you won't just experience the Kinesthetic Games studio, but we will show you around the various studios of Guildford, the Mecca of games development in the UK, where you'll get to meet and greet with prominent games developers (participating studios TBA). 

ALSO the LEGEND Reward. 

ALSO the IMMORTAL Reward.

ALSO... no, that's everything.

MOOK YAN JONG: A beautiful, high quality, custom Mook Yan Jong (WOODEN DUMMY) designed according to your needs with an optional \u529f\u592b\u5de8\u661f (Kung Fu Superstar) engraving + Exclusive "Wooden Dummy Forms" In Game Content + IMMORTAL Reward + LEGEND Reward

SIFU: Be one of the first individuals/martial art schools/organisations to join our "Kung Fu Superstar\u2122 Training Partners" programme. We will work together to create training scenarios and other content around your specific style and curriculum needs, with a view to make it available through the game as an officially licensed product. Get in touch for details to ensure you don't miss out on early access to the definitive martial arts gaming platform + IMMORTAL Reward + LEGEND Reward

DIRECTOR: Playing Fight Choreography Sequences is cool and all, but you're actually more interested in *building* them. Well, as a Licensee of our "Fight Choreography Engine" technology, you can! Whether you're a production house looking to previsualise the fight sequences of your action film in a fast and intuitive way or a mod team looking to create the next big machinima hit, our tools will help you unleash your creativity through ultra fast iteration. Pledging at this level won't just ensure you get a lifetime License for the FCE suite of tools, you will also get early tech previews so you can request features, suggest improvements and help shape this innovative and groundbreaking technology. Get in touch for details!
